flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{User selects payment option}
    B -->|Yes| C[User enters payment details]
    B -->|No| D[User cancels transaction]
    C --> E{Payment method selected}
    E -->|WhatsApp Pay| F[Process payment through WhatsApp Pay]
    E -->|Other| G[Redirect to alternative payment method]
    F --> H{Payment successful?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Transaction completed]
    H -->|No| J[Show error message]
    J --> K[User retries payment]
    K --> C
    D --> L[End]
    I --> L
    G --> L